replies.body:
This leads me the believe this was caused by your client disconnecting from the servers entirely. This was likely the result of an unstable connection to the servers, and could be affected by network configurations that conflict with League. As a first step, I recommend working through the solutions in our [connection guide.
](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752664-Troubleshooting-Connection-Issues)

Let me know if those steps helped.
